# Huskies Pro — Org Baseline

This repo is part of the **huskies-pro** mono-org. The parent workspace is at `../` and contains 67+ sibling repos, each an independent git repository for one service or project.

## HuskyNet-MCP Gateway

AI tools can connect to **Porygon:8100** — a shared MCP gateway with 11 backends and ~117 tools: Home Assistant, Fully Kiosk, Portainer, Loki, MQTT, Obsidian, arr-suite (Sonarr/Radarr/Prowlarr/Bazarr/Overseerr/Plex), memory, sequential-thinking, web-search, context7, and time.

