## Safety

- **Checkpoint before writes:** Call `ha_create_checkpoint` before any HA write operations
- **Never commit secrets:** `*.env` files are gitignored org-wide. Use `<<PLACEHOLDER>>` pattern in version-controlled files
- **This repo is independent:** it has its own git remote and history. Commit and push from within this directory
